					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is pretty good, I can see why it is doing well in the ratings. I like the tone set here where the Foundation actually manages to save the world from a horrible fate, but you still manage to feel uncomfortable at the end - it's very on-brand for SCP. +1</p> 
