					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13126192#post-4542148</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13126192/scp-5408#post-4542148</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2020 12:03:54 +0000</pubDate>
								<wikidot:authorUserId>3146689</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is very good. There's a type of article that leans towards an interesting subversion at the end, and then there's one that's more about good writing and intrigue at the beginning and the middle. This one, however, does both. Admittedly, the outcome was a bit predictable with the first transmission that marketed the place, but in general, the piece was well-written enough for me to still enjoy it. +1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
