						 <p>tl;dr: Hellstar Remina leaves a Yelp review.</p> <p>All jokes aside, easy +1. What a horrifying concept, and the juxtaposition between this cosmic planet-eater's horrific goal of chowing down on Earth and the anodyne language used in the review + advertisement is perfection.</p> 
